## Installation and Execution

This project is provided for academic evaluation purposes.  
The following steps describe how to run the system locally.

### Backend Setup
cd backend
npm install


Create a .env file in the backend directory and configure the required
environment variables.
(Note: The .env file is not included in the repository for security reasons.)

Seed the initial data categories:
   node scripts/seedDataCategories.js

Start the backend server:
    npm run dev

### Frontend Setup
    cd frontend
    npm install
    npm run dev
